input_str: Throughout history, entrepreneurs have been celebrated in the best of times and demonized in the worst. Even today, political and social arguments over the real benefits provided by these entrepreneurs remain an ongoing feature in public debate. One thing that receives scant attention, however, is the extent to which centralized fiat monetary policy impacts entrepreneurs.
